{"type":"message","id":"22e33faf","parentId":"59acb6c0","timestamp":"2026-03-24T16:20:53.745Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_39jz8zgyd23g_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 5276\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=2951\n[file inferred from ACTION] experiment\n[mutation proposed] experiment\n[master 868a55b] pulse: 2026-03-24 122016\n 6 files changed, 374 insertions(+), 99 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 122016.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 122016.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 121914.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 122016 - The CFI analysis revealed that 94.3% of frequency-invariants have CFI<0.7 (noise/metaprogramming artifacts), yet current compression is frequency-based only. No implementation exists yet for CFI-weighted compression comparison."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"tidy-harbor","total":10,"totalLines":10,"totalChars":732,"truncated":false,"exitCode":0,"name":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774369253743}}
